	<datafield ind1="1" ind2="0" tag="245">
		<subfield code="6">880-02</subfield>
		<subfield code="a">Tārīkh al-Imām al-Shāfi‘ī :</subfield>
		<subfield code="b">bi-qalamihi wa-mā katabahu ‘an nafsih wa-tashmulu sabab ḥuḍūrihi li-Miṣr wa-riḥlatihi ilá al-Madīnah wa-Makkah wa-al-Kūfah wa-al-‘Irāq wa-mā laqāh /</subfield>
		<subfield code="c">riwāyah ‘an Abī Bakr Muḥammad ibn al-Mundhir ‘an Abī Muḥammad al-Rabī‘ al-Murādī ‘an al-Shāfi‘ī nafsahu, wa-fī awwalihā samā‘ lil-‘Allāmah al-Juwaynī wa-bi-ākhirihā samā‘ ayḍan lil-‘Allāmah al-Juwānī al-nassābah naqīb al-nuqabā’. Wa-yalīhi Tārīkh shāmil lil-Imām al-Shāfi‘ī ayḍan wa-dhikr manāqibihi wa-karāmātihi wa-madhabayhi al-qadīm wa-al-jadīd wa-sabab majī’ihi li-Miṣr wa-mā ḥadathah fī wafātihi bihā / min ta’līf al-‘allāmah al-‘ālim ṣāḥib al-darajatayn dhī al-samāḥah wa-al-faḍīlah al-ustādh al-kabīr al-ḥabr al-baḥr al-Sayyid Ḥusayn Muḥammad al-Rifā‘ī al-Shāfi‘ī al-Ḥanafī, min kibār ulamā’ al-Azhar wa-al-mushrif al-‘ām ‘alá ma‘āriḍ Dār al-Kutub al-Miṣrīyah bi-al-Qāhirah wa-ra’īs Rābiṭat al-Ashrāf al-Kubrá al-‘alamīyah.</subfield>
	</datafield>
